---
const imageUrl = "/fotos/AVATAR.jpg";

const languages = [
  { src: "/fotos/html.png", link: "https://developer.mozilla.org/es/docs/Web/HTML"},
  { src: "/fotos/js.png", link: "https://developer.mozilla.org/es/docs/Web/JavaScript"},
  { src: "/fotos/php.png", link: "https://www.php.net/" },
];

---

<section class="flex flex-col-reverse items-center justify-center p-8 font-mono md:flex-row md:p-8 lg:p-16 gap-20">
  <div class="max-w-xl text-lg text-center md:max-w-md md:text-base md:text-left lg:max-w-xl lg:text-2xl">
    <p class="text-2xl leading-relaxed md:text-lg lg:text-3xl">
      Soy Alexandro, desarrollador especializado en programación. Me apasiona crear soluciones eficientes y optimizadas, siempre buscando aprender nuevas tecnologías.
      Tengo experiencia en diversos lenguajes algunos de ellos son:
    </p>

    <div class="flex justify-center md:justify-start gap-6 mt-6">
      {languages.map(lang => (
        <a href={lang.link} target="_blank" class="transition-transform transform hover:scale-110">
          <img src={lang.src} />
        </a>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="relative">
    <img src={imageUrl} alt="Mi foto"
      class="w-[250px] h-[250px] rounded-full shadow-lg object-cover mx-auto 
             md:w-[400px] md:h-[400px] lg:w-[500px] lg:h-[500px] 
             animate-floating translate-y-[-15px]" />
    
    <img src="/fotos/sh.png" alt="Shuriken"
      class="absolute w-12 h-12 left-[-45px] top-[-45px] animate-shuriken" />

    <img src="/fotos/sh.png" alt="Shuriken"
      class="absolute w-12 h-12 right-[-45px] top-[-45px] animate-shuriken" />

    <img src="/fotos/sh.png" alt="Shuriken"
      class="absolute w-12 h-12 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 bottom-[-45px] animate-shuriken" />
  </div>
</section>
